[h1]Phobos' Chemistry Pathways — Changelog[/h1]

[h2]v0.26.0 — Recipe Heat Gating Fix (2026-03-05)[/h2]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]hotFluidContainer checked wrong item[/b] — Recipes requiring hot water (salt crystallisation, charcoal purification, fat rendering, soap-making, bandage sterilisation, etc.) failed when using certain water containers (petrol cans, jars, bottles) even when a hot pot was on the stove. Root cause: the heat check tested the water source container instead of the heated vessel. 23 recipes across 5 files now use a merged single-item pattern where the container on the stove provides both water and heat.
[*] [b]Empty FluidContainers showed "(Worn)"[/b] — Drained FluidContainers retained purity-stamped condition, causing PZ to display "(Worn)" on empty containers. Condition now resets to maximum when fluid is fully consumed.
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.15.0+[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.25.0 — Salt Extraction & B42 Fluid Syntax (2026-03-05)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Salt Extraction Pathway[/b] — 6 new recipes: collect brine from water wells, concentrate brine (2 tiers), crystallize salt (2 tiers), purify table salt. Right-click water wells to begin collection.
[*] [b]4 new items[/b] — Brine, ConcentratedBrine, RockSalt, TableSalt
[*] [b]1 new fluid[/b] — Brine (9 fluids total)
[*] [b]Entity Rebinding[/b] — Pre-existing concrete mixer workstations automatically updated on game load
[/list]

[h3]Technical Improvements[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]B42 Native Fluid Syntax[/b] — All 133 FluidContainer recipe inputs converted to B42's native -fluid (drain) and +fluid (fill) syntax. Improved compatibility with Build 42's fluid container system.
[*] Recipes now use InHandCraft;Cooking tags for proper player inventory routing of filled containers
[/list]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Fluid recipe outputs[/b] — Filled containers from crafting now correctly appear in player inventory instead of ground/proximity inventory
[*] FluidCategory enum error fixed (removed invalid Triglyceride category)
[*] -fluid input ordering fixed for B42 container-line constraints
[*] Base.GasCan removed (does not exist in B42)
[*] CraftBench entity definitions fixed (xuiSkin, CraftLogic, rotation sprites)
[*] Brine collection MP sync (stopSound + sendItemStats)
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Recipe count: 198 to 204
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.14.0+[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.24.0 — In-Game Guide & Changelog Popups (2026-02-23)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Welcome Guide[/b] — First-time tutorial popup on new characters explaining PCP's chemistry pathways, sandbox options, and getting started. "Don't show again" checkbox with per-character persistence.
[*] [b]Changelog Popup[/b] — Version-based "What's New" popup on updates, showing only changes since your last played version.
[/list]

[h3]Critical Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]FluidContainer -fluid binding cascade[/b] — Fixed 4 cascading CTDs caused by B42 -fluid input rules. Wildcards ([*]) before -fluid lines greedily matched FluidContainer items, stealing them from designated input slots. 13 hotFluidContainer recipes now use tags[base:cookable] instead.
[*] [b]base:smallblade NPE[/b] — Replaced invalid weapon Category tag with correct ItemTags (base:sharpknife;base:scissors) in PCPCutPlasticScrap. The old tag caused an NPE CTD on world load.
[*] Invalid item IDs in mixer recipes corrected (Base.Blackpowder, Base.WoodVinegar)
[*] Mixer recipe -fluid input ordering fixed for B42 constraints
[*] MineralFeedSupplement ConditionMax corrected from 1 to 100
[*] Workstation translation keys added for PCP_ConcreteMixer
[*] Guide popup colour tag spacing fixed
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.13.0+[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.23.0 — Concrete Mixer Workstation (2026-02-23)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Concrete Mixer[/b] — Powered CraftBench entity for industrial-scale processing. Build from a metal drum + salvaged motor + welding equipment (Metalworking:4). Requires electricity (grid or generator). Generator fuel drains during crafting.
[*] [b]13 new recipes[/b] in PhobosIndustrialChem crafting category:
  — [b]Construction[/b] (6): Concrete, Clay Cement, Mortar, Stucco, Reinforced Concrete, Fireclay
  — [b]Bulk Chemistry[/b] (5): Blackpowder, Biodiesel, Soap, Compost, Wood Vinegar
  — [b]Processing[/b] (1): Plaster Powder
  — [b]Fabrication[/b] (1): Build Concrete Mixer
[*] [b]4 new items[/b] — MortarMix, StuccoMix, ReinforcedConcrete, Fireclay
[*] [b]3 new sandbox options[/b] — EnableConcreteMixer, ConcreteMixerYieldBonus, MixerFuelDrainRate
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Recipe count: 185 to 198
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.12.0+[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.22.0 — Agriculture & Downstream Pathways (2026-02-22)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]31 new recipes[/b] across 6 downstream pathways connecting PCP intermediates to vanilla gameplay:
  — [b]Garden Pest Sprays[/b] (3): Sulphur Fungicide (cures Mildew), Insecticidal Soap (cures Aphids), Potash Foliar (cures Flies) — functional B42 farming sprays
  — [b]Mineral Feed Supplements[/b] (3): BoneChar + Calcite animal feed
  — [b]Water Purification[/b] (4): Activated charcoal filters, purification tablets, gas mask filter recharging
  — [b]Epoxy Resin[/b] (6): WoodTar + Glycerol structural adhesive
  — [b]Fire-Starting[/b] (7): Lighter fluid, matchboxes, slug repellent, duct tape
  — [b]Chemical Processing[/b] (8): Leather tanning, plaster powder, wood vinegar
[*] [b]3 new FluidContainer items[/b] — Gardening sprays (functional crop cures)
[*] [b]7 new tradeable items[/b] for Dynamic Trading (34 total)
[*] Pneumonia added to caustic vapour and resin fumes hazard profiles
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Recipe count: 154 to 185
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.11.0+[/b]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.21.3 — DT Price Rebalance (2026-02-21)[/h2]
[list]
[*] All Dynamic Trading item prices rebalanced and anchored to vanilla DT basePrices. Key increases across processing chains (e.g. SulphuricAcidJar 35 to 80, biodiesel chain 25/40/80 to 55/80/120). Stock ranges tightened on high-value items.
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.21.2 — Purity Sync Fix (2026-02-21)[/h2]
[list]
[*] Purity now visible immediately after crafting — added sendItemStats() call after setCondition() for instant client UI sync (previously delayed until next automatic sync cycle).
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v0.21.1 — Cooking & Purity Fixes (2026-02-21)[/h2]
[list]
[*] [b]Cooking-pot recipes no longer craftable cold[/b] — All 19 PhobosKitchenChem recipes now properly require heat: 12 wet-heat recipes use hotFluidContainer (must heat pot on stove first), 7 dry-heat recipes use openFire (campfire, fireplace, or stove nearby).
[*] [b]Purity crash on vanilla-output recipes[/b] — Recycling recipes outputting vanilla items (Fertilizer, Soap, Glue, etc.) no longer crash when purity system is enabled. Added module-prefix guard; removed 10 dead purity callbacks.
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]Summary[/h2]
[list]
[*] [b]204 recipes[/b] across 9 pathways — Blackpowder, Biodiesel, Fat Rendering, Soap, Bone Char, Salt Extraction, Recycling, Agriculture, Concrete Mixer
[*] [b]47 items[/b], [b]34 tradeable items[/b], [b]5 skill books[/b], [b]9 fluids[/b]
[*] [b]16 sandbox options[/b], [b]168 OnCreate callbacks[/b]
[*] New since v0.25.0: hotFluidContainer heat gating fix, empty container condition reset
[*] Requires PhobosLib 1.15.0+ and zReVaccin 3
[/list]
